{"id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0013","text":"下半身也凌空雙腳不貼地","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["飄飄欲仙","興奮","失重"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["下半身","凌空","不貼地"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,3,5,0,3,3,4,3,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["haa6","bun3","san1","jaa5","ling4","hung1","soeng1","goek3","bat1","tip3","dei6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"下半身","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"凌空","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"雙腳","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不貼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"地","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"延續上一行的感覺，「凌空」、「不貼地」進一步加強了身體失控、飄浮的意象，表達極致的興奮。"},"source":{"title":"臭男人","artists":["謝安琪"],"lyricists":["周博賢"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4618","prev_line_id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0014","text":"是你這臭男人使我天空飛","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","影響","興奮"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["臭男人","天空飛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,5,4,0,0,9,5,3,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["si6","nei5","ze5","cau3","naam4","jan4","si2","ngo5","tin1","hung1","fei1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"臭男人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"使","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"天空","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"飛","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"直接點名「臭男人」，但卻是使自己「天空飛」的原因，形成一種反差，強調對方獨特的吸引力。"},"source":{"title":"臭男人","artists":["謝安琪"],"lyricists":["周博賢"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4618","prev_line_id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_6LCi5a6J55Cq_NDYxOA_0015","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
